titles.en: DIY - How to Lighten Dark lips Naturally

descriptions.en:
Here is an easy method to brighten lips from easily available ingredients in your kitchen shared by Super Princess Jo. 

Ingredients:
rose petal
milk
saffron
cotton

Method:
Soak a few dry or fresh rose petals in raw milk for upto one hour. Add a pinch of saffron to it. Apply the mixture on your lips with cotton or Q tips-and leave it on for about 15 minutes to overnight. Do this everyday until desire color is achieved.
